I've heard of this!

00:09:22.354 --> 00:09:25.065 position:50% align:center
It's an important promotion
for <i>The Ronaldo Chronicles</i> .

00:09:25.148 --> 00:09:27.859 position:50% align:center
So, please do your best
to not screw this up.

00:09:27.942 --> 00:09:30.570 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO whimpers, groans]

00:09:30.653 --> 00:09:32.155 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Dammit!

00:09:32.238 --> 00:09:35.033 position:50% align:center
If Handa finds out about this,
it's gonna be a total disaster!

00:09:35.116 --> 00:09:38.495 position:50% align:center
And if this fails, Mr. Fukuma
will chop me to pieces!

00:09:38.578 --> 00:09:39.746 position:50% align:center
Somehow I need
to get through this

00:09:39.829 --> 00:09:42.582 position:50% align:center
without incident
and keep the peace!

00:09:42.665 --> 00:09:45.543 position:50% align:center
No way I'll let this end
peacefully, Ronaldo!

00:09:45.627 --> 00:09:48.505 position:50% align:center
Things sure are getting
interesting aren't they, John?

00:09:48.588 --> 00:09:50.715 position:50% align:center
I was wondering why you
called me so suddenly,

00:09:50.799 --> 00:09:53.051 position:50% align:center
but it's obvious now.

00:09:53.134 --> 00:09:56.221 position:50% align:center
I'm surprised you're
just sneaking around though.

00:09:56.304 --> 00:09:57.889 position:50% align:center
I thought for sure
you would go charging in

00:09:57.972 --> 00:09:59.432 position:50% align:center
with an anti-tank gun
or something.

00:09:59.516 --> 00:10:01.935 position:50% align:center
Bastard, what exactly
do you think I am?

00:10:02.018 --> 00:10:03.645 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
A landmine with legs.

00:10:03.728 --> 00:10:05.397 position:50% align:center
Sand.

00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:07.065 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
If I beat up Ronaldo right now,

00:10:07.148 --> 00:10:09.067 position:50% align:center
I'll make my mom sad!

00:10:09.150 --> 00:10:12.529 position:50% align:center
And she's been
looking fo-fo-fo--

00:10:12.612 --> 00:10:15.198 position:50% align:center
She's been looking
forward to this!

00:10:15.281 --> 00:10:17.909 position:50% align:center
And yet! If I can expose
him while he's with her,

00:10:17.992 --> 00:10:20.620 position:50% align:center
she'll be disillusioned
and come to her senses!

00:10:20.704 --> 00:10:21.621 position:50% align:center
That's right!

00:10:21.705 --> 00:10:23.581 position:50% align:center
This is my chance!
My big chance!

00:10:23.665 --> 00:10:26.084 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Cold sweat, cold sweat.

00:10:27.544 --> 00:10:29.504 position:50% align:center
Oh, um, are you all
right with human food,

00:10:29.587 --> 00:10:31.047 position:50% align:center
or should we get something else?

00:10:31.131 --> 00:10:32.298 position:50% align:center
[AKEMI]
That's fine.

00:10:32.382 --> 00:10:34.718 position:50% align:center
So, how exactly are you
planning to expose him?

00:10:34.801 --> 00:10:36.970 position:50% align:center
[HANDA chuckles] These kinds
of dates are all the same--

00:10:37.053 --> 00:10:39.180 position:50% align:center
they usually involve
a meal and a walk.

00:10:39.264 --> 00:10:42.600 position:50% align:center
My guess is, they'll prob'ly go
to the restaurant up ahead.

00:10:42.684 --> 00:10:44.769 position:50% align:center
See? Called it.

00:10:44.853 --> 00:10:48.106 position:50% align:center
You were right on the money!
Now what do you plan to do?

00:10:48.189 --> 00:10:49.566 position:50% align:center
I'm going to switch out his food

00:10:49.649 --> 00:10:51.609 position:50% align:center
with this special
celery Hamburg steak!

00:10:51.693 --> 00:10:53.319 position:50% align:center
Your plan's getting
quite sloppy!

00:10:53.403 --> 00:10:55.030 position:50% align:center
[HANDA] He'll take
one bite and go, "Gah!"

00:10:55.113 --> 00:10:58.450 position:50% align:center
Mom'll think it's gross!
It's an infallible plan!

00:10:58.533 --> 00:10:59.617 position:50% align:center
Come on, we're going in.

00:10:59.701 --> 00:11:02.162 position:50% align:center
Man, this crap is even
dumber than usual!

00:11:02.245 --> 00:11:04.330 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
I'm Handa. I work here now.

00:11:06.082 --> 00:11:08.168 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] So yeah, this is,
like, really a restaurant, huh?

00:11:08.251 --> 00:11:11.212 position:50% align:center
That bastard, sitting there,
chatting with my mom!

00:11:11.296 --> 00:11:13.923 position:50% align:center
I'll wipe that stupid look
off your face, Ronaldo!

00:11:14.007 --> 00:11:16.843 position:50% align:center
This celery hamburg steak
will do the trick.

00:11:16.926 --> 00:11:18.011 position:50% align:center
What the--?

00:11:18.094 --> 00:11:19.262 position:50% align:center
[FAN 07B]
We'll be eating that, thanks!

00:11:19.346 --> 00:11:20.847 position:50% align:center
[HANDA gasps]

00:11:20.930 --> 00:11:22.349 position:50% align:center
I don't know what you're trying,
but it ain't gonna work, boy.

00:11:22.432 --> 00:11:25.268 position:50% align:center
Akemi's date with Ronaldo
the Great won't be sabotaged!

00:11:25.352 --> 00:11:28.688 position:50% align:center
[HANDA groans]
A surprise ambush.

00:11:28.772 --> 00:11:31.399 position:50% align:center
[WAITER 07A] Thanks for waiting.
Chef's special: hamburg steak.

00:11:31.483 --> 00:11:32.233 position:50% align:center
[HANDA yelps]

00:11:32.317 --> 00:11:33.985 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
No!

00:11:34.069 --> 00:11:35.403 position:50% align:center
Enjoy.

00:11:35.487 --> 00:11:37.447 position:50% align:center
Chef uses a whole stalk of
celery in the ground beef.

00:11:37.530 --> 00:11:38.907 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO groans]

00:11:38.990 --> 00:11:40.658 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Uhh...

00:11:40.742 --> 00:11:42.160 position:50% align:center
Oh, Ronaldo, are you all right?

00:11:42.243 --> 00:11:43.787 position:50% align:center
Uh, yeah. I'm fine.

00:11:43.870 --> 00:11:45.955 position:50% align:center
I just really don't like celery.

00:11:46.039 --> 00:11:48.416 position:50% align:center
I'm a puking worm who barfs
when I don't like something,

00:11:48.500 --> 00:11:50.669 position:50% align:center
so feel free to ridicule me.

00:11:52.337 --> 00:11:54.798 position:50% align:center
Everyone has things
they don't like to eat.

00:11:54.881 --> 00:11:57.175 position:50% align:center
I would never
scorn you for that.

00:11:57.258 --> 00:12:00.136 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO gasps]
So kind.

00:12:00.220 --> 00:12:02.347 position:50% align:center
I can't believe
you're Handa's mom.

00:12:02.430 --> 00:12:04.849 position:50% align:center
I mean, it is written on
page 52 of volume one

00:12:04.933 --> 00:12:05.934 position:50% align:center
that you don't like celery,

00:12:06.017 --> 00:12:07.435 position:50% align:center
so I'm happy to find out
that it's true!

00:12:07.519 --> 00:12:09.145 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Yup, you're Handa's mom.

00:12:09.229 --> 00:12:10.730 position:50% align:center
Oh, can I commemorate
with a photo?

00:12:10.814 --> 00:12:12.607 position:50% align:center
I'd rather you not!

00:12:12.691 --> 00:12:14.359 position:50% align:center
[MANAGER 07A]
Thank you for coming.

00:12:14.442 --> 00:12:17.445 position:50% align:center
[HANDA growls]
She geeked! That's Mom for you.

00:12:17.529 --> 00:12:19.989 position:50% align:center
Damn it, next! Let's go, Draluc!

00:12:20.073 --> 00:12:22.283 position:50% align:center
I think in order to make
the celery flavor bolder,

00:12:22.367 --> 00:12:24.661 position:50% align:center
you should add a little-- Sand!

00:12:24.744 --> 00:12:25.954 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
Draluc!

00:12:26.037 --> 00:12:27.956 position:50% align:center
[FAN 07A]
Come on, after them!

00:12:28.039 --> 00:12:30.250 position:50% align:center
[JOHN cries]

00:12:32.127 --> 00:12:33.545 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Shall we go sit on a bench?

00:12:33.628 --> 00:12:34.671 position:50% align:center
Sure.

00:12:34.754 --> 00:12:36.214 position:50% align:center
Now they're eating
crepes like lovers?

00:12:36.297 --> 00:12:38.299 position:50% align:center
Just wait, Ronaldo! You're dead!

00:12:38.383 --> 00:12:40.468 position:50% align:center
Right, what's next
up on the agenda?

00:12:40.552 --> 00:12:43.555 position:50% align:center
[HANDA] Mom has a kind, just
heart, pure as driven snow.

00:12:43.638 --> 00:12:46.307 position:50% align:center
She feels deep rage for those
who pick on kids and animals.

00:12:46.391 --> 00:12:47.976 position:50% align:center
How'd her son
turn out like this?

00:12:48.059 --> 00:12:49.394 position:50% align:center
So, what now?

00:12:49.477 --> 00:12:52.689 position:50% align:center
Okay, so first, you have
to transform into a cute bat.

00:12:52.772 --> 00:12:56.026 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Oh, great.
I can see where this is going.

00:12:56.109 --> 00:12:58.445 position:50% align:center
[AKEMI]
Did that cleanse your palate?

00:12:58.528 --> 00:13:01.239 position:50% align:center
Uh! Oh, please forget
what happened earlier.

00:13:01.322 --> 00:13:02.490 position:50% align:center
[AKEMI giggles]

00:13:02.574 --> 00:13:04.200 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Scuttle,
scuttle, scuttle, scuttle.

00:13:04.284 --> 00:13:05.744 position:50% align:center
Glance.

00:13:05.827 --> 00:13:09.914 position:50% align:center
Scuttle, scuttle,
scuttle, scuttle, scuttle.

00:13:09.998 --> 00:13:11.833 position:50% align:center
Scuttle, scuttle,
scuttle, scuttle-- Sand!

00:13:11.916 --> 00:13:15.920 position:50% align:center
Dammit, Draluc, no! What the
hell was that gross thing?

00:13:16.004 --> 00:13:18.465 position:50% align:center
Even Gautama Buddha
would've killed that!

00:13:18.548 --> 00:13:20.842 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] I have a tendency to
fail at my transformations.

00:13:20.925 --> 00:13:22.677 position:50% align:center
[phone rings]

00:13:22.761 --> 00:13:24.346 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Ronaldo is seriously pissed.

00:13:24.429 --> 00:13:25.972 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
Good! Let him be!

00:13:26.056 --> 00:13:28.058 position:50% align:center
I'll have to use
my ultimate weapon!

00:13:28.141 --> 00:13:30.185 position:50% align:center
[LAND CLIONE squeals]

00:13:30.268 --> 00:13:33.521 position:50% align:center
[HANDA] Expose your high-cut-
leg-wearing self, Ronaldo!

00:13:33.605 --> 00:13:35.231 position:50% align:center
Go! Go get Ronaldo, okay?

00:13:35.315 --> 00:13:36.107 position:50% align:center
[LAND CLIONE squeals]

00:13:36.191 --> 00:13:38.568 position:50% align:center
[LAND CLIONE gasps]
Water!

00:13:38.651 --> 00:13:40.195 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
No. Wha--? No!

00:13:40.278 --> 00:13:43.656 position:50% align:center
What? Oh! Uh. Aw...

00:13:43.740 --> 00:13:45.992 position:50% align:center
Damn, I failed. I failed again.

00:13:46.076 --> 00:13:48.161 position:50% align:center
Give up already.
Go get some sleep.

00:13:48.244 --> 00:13:49.746 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaks]

00:13:52.665 --> 00:13:53.291 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO grunts]

00:13:53.375 --> 00:13:55.627 position:50% align:center
Uh...

00:13:55.710 --> 00:13:56.670 position:50% align:center
[LAND CLIONE roars]

00:13:56.753 --> 00:13:58.171 position:50% align:center
[HANDA gasps]
No.

00:13:58.254 --> 00:13:59.464 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Sand!
--[HANDA] Mom, look out!

00:13:59.547 --> 00:14:01.091 position:50% align:center
[AKEMI gasps]

00:14:01.966 --> 00:14:05.345 position:50% align:center
[LAND CLIONE snarls, groans]

00:14:05.428 --> 00:14:08.723 position:50% align:center
[LAND CLIONE groans]

00:14:08.807 --> 00:14:10.266 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:14:14.062 --> 00:14:16.773 position:50% align:center
Jeez, what the heck
was that all about?

00:14:18.441 --> 00:14:20.819 position:50% align:center
Are you all right, Akemi?

00:14:20.902 --> 00:14:22.612 position:50% align:center
You're amazing.

00:14:22.696 --> 00:14:24.864 position:50% align:center
Oh, Ronaldo the Great,
thank you so much!

00:14:24.948 --> 00:14:27.409 position:50% align:center
You're the best hunter!

00:14:27.492 --> 00:14:28.785 position:50% align:center
Momo? That you?

00:14:28.868 --> 00:14:30.078 position:50% align:center
What are you doing here?

00:14:30.161 --> 00:14:32.247 position:50% align:center
Huh?! Why... I, uh--

00:14:32.330 --> 00:14:33.331 position:50% align:center
[AKEMI gasps]
Did you want to meet

00:14:33.415 --> 00:14:35.166 position:50% align:center
Ronaldo the Great, too, Momo?

00:14:35.250 --> 00:14:36.876 position:50% align:center
I'm sorry if I hogged him.

00:14:36.960 --> 00:14:38.044 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:14:38.128 --> 00:14:39.504 position:50% align:center
So was that why you
were stalking them?

00:14:39.587 --> 00:14:40.755 position:50% align:center
Just jealous of your mom?

00:14:40.839 --> 00:14:42.048 position:50% align:center
How adorable!

00:14:42.132 --> 00:14:43.299 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:14:43.383 --> 00:14:44.843 position:50% align:center
My son's a big fan, too!

00:14:44.926 --> 00:14:46.636 position:50% align:center
Would you mind giving
him a handshake?

00:14:46.720 --> 00:14:48.304 position:50% align:center
[HANDA gasps]

00:14:48.388 --> 00:14:50.015 position:50% align:center
Uh...

00:14:50.098 --> 00:14:52.308 position:50% align:center
Hello...

00:14:52.392 --> 00:14:54.394 position:50% align:center
[HANDA growls]

00:14:54.477 --> 00:14:55.520 position:50% align:center
[AKEMI giggles]

00:14:55.603 --> 00:15:00.984 position:50% align:center
[HANDA groaning]

00:15:02.569 --> 00:15:07.323 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
Why?!

00:15:19.627 --> 00:15:21.713 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO groans]

00:15:22.714 --> 00:15:25.467 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Hey, Ronaldo! I'm so bored!

00:15:25.550 --> 00:15:27.802 position:50% align:center
Wanna play Vario Kart? Hm?

00:15:32.182 --> 00:15:34.434 position:50% align:center
Where are you going?
To Sandbucks?

00:15:34.517 --> 00:15:35.560 position:50% align:center
I wanna come, too.

00:15:35.643 --> 00:15:36.686 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaking]

00:15:36.770 --> 00:15:39.105 position:50% align:center
I even practiced a
spell for Sandbucks:

00:15:39.189 --> 00:15:41.358 position:50% align:center
Venti mocha, add shots of
hazelnut, vanilla, almond,

00:15:41.441 --> 00:15:44.486 position:50% align:center
and caramel with extra whip
and caramel sauce.

00:15:44.569 --> 00:15:46.404 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] Can you watch this
idiot for me for a while?

00:15:46.488 --> 00:15:48.448 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC screams]

00:15:49.949 --> 00:15:52.660 position:50% align:center
Finally, I can concentrate
on my writing.

00:15:52.744 --> 00:15:53.495 position:50% align:center
[JOHN grunts]

00:15:53.578 --> 00:15:55.413 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Hm?

00:15:55.497 --> 00:15:58.792 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS]
Hm? Welcome back.

00:15:58.875 --> 00:16:00.877 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS groans]

00:16:00.960 --> 00:16:03.630 position:50% align:center
Bastard, how did
you get in here--?

00:16:03.713 --> 00:16:06.299 position:50% align:center
What the--? Why isn't he dead?

00:16:06.383 --> 00:16:07.967 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS]
Is that any way to be hospitable

00:16:08.051 --> 00:16:09.886 position:50% align:center
toward your guests, Paul?

00:16:09.969 --> 00:16:12.722 position:50% align:center
Uh! You're Draluc's old man!

00:16:12.806 --> 00:16:16.059 position:50% align:center
Long time no see, Paul--
I mean, Hunter Ronaldo!

00:16:16.142 --> 00:16:17.394 position:50% align:center
Go home!

00:16:17.477 --> 00:16:19.646 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS] Can't we just
talk a little longer?

00:16:19.729 --> 00:16:22.023 position:50% align:center
What do you want
barging in like this?

00:16:22.107 --> 00:16:24.734 position:50% align:center
Why, I came to see
my son, naturally.

00:16:24.818 --> 00:16:26.069 position:50% align:center
What of it?

00:16:26.152 --> 00:16:27.153 position:50% align:center
Are you saying I'm wrong

00:16:27.237 --> 00:16:29.364 position:50% align:center
for coming all this way
to visit my boy?

00:16:29.447 --> 00:16:32.617 position:50% align:center
You are wrong for breaking
and entering and tea burgling!

00:16:32.701 --> 00:16:34.911 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS]
Anyway, where is Draluc?

00:16:34.994 --> 00:16:37.831 position:50% align:center
Oh, he-- He went out.
You just missed him!

00:16:37.914 --> 00:16:40.625 position:50% align:center
He, um... He's helping some
underprivileged children

00:16:40.709 --> 00:16:41.876 position:50% align:center
learn life skills.

00:16:41.960 --> 00:16:44.838 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS]
I expect no less from my son!

00:16:44.921 --> 00:16:47.132 position:50% align:center
Too bad I missed him, though.

00:16:47.215 --> 00:16:49.384 position:50% align:center
And I brought all
these presents for him.

00:16:49.467 --> 00:16:51.720 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] Being spoiled
for 200 years'd make anyone

00:16:51.803 --> 00:16:53.346 position:50% align:center
turn out like Draluc.

00:16:53.430 --> 00:16:54.806 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS] I have a present
for you, too, John.

00:16:54.889 --> 00:16:56.307 position:50% align:center
The turn table you wanted.

00:16:56.391 --> 00:16:58.059 position:50% align:center
--[JOHN squeaks]
--[RONALDO] John's a DJ?

00:16:58.143 --> 00:17:00.770 position:50% align:center
I got you this, Paul.
From the 100-yen store.

00:17:00.854 --> 00:17:02.480 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS yelps]

00:17:02.564 --> 00:17:03.690 position:50% align:center
Just go home, damn it!

00:17:03.773 --> 00:17:05.984 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS groans]
You leave me no choice.

00:17:06.067 --> 00:17:07.861 position:50% align:center
I won't move until
Draluc gets back!

00:17:07.944 --> 00:17:09.487 position:50% align:center
Did you hear what I said?

00:17:09.571 --> 00:17:11.281 position:50% align:center
Cruelest hunter of them all!

00:17:11.364 --> 00:17:13.450 position:50% align:center
I won't move until he's back
except for this sweet dance!

00:17:13.533 --> 00:17:14.993 position:50% align:center
Don't dance!

00:17:15.076 --> 00:17:16.578 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Damn it.

00:17:16.661 --> 00:17:18.872 position:50% align:center
Oh well, I'll just
ignore him. Ignore him!

00:17:18.955 --> 00:17:20.915 position:50% align:center
Pretend he's
not there and focus.

00:17:20.999 --> 00:17:23.209 position:50% align:center
[keyboard clacking]

00:17:23.293 --> 00:17:26.296 position:50% align:center
What's that? The next book
of <i>The Ronaldo Chronicles</i> ?

00:17:26.379 --> 00:17:28.673 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] Stay strong!
If you react, you lose!

00:17:28.757 --> 00:17:29.924 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS]
Hmm. Let's see.

00:17:30.008 --> 00:17:31.885 position:50% align:center
"And then I threw
a ball right at his face."

00:17:31.968 --> 00:17:33.511 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Don't read it!

00:17:33.595 --> 00:17:35.638 position:50% align:center
I do have some notes.
I have to say,

00:17:35.722 --> 00:17:37.682 position:50% align:center
I do not think you've
done nearly enough research

00:17:37.766 --> 00:17:38.933 position:50% align:center
about vampires.

00:17:39.017 --> 00:17:41.019 position:50% align:center
Especially with how
you depict Draluc!

00:17:41.102 --> 00:17:43.563 position:50% align:center
You should write more
details about my son.

00:17:43.646 --> 00:17:45.065 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
I want to punch him so hard.

00:17:45.148 --> 00:17:47.942 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS] I brought something that
I thought could help you.

00:17:48.026 --> 00:17:48.985 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Hm?

00:17:49.069 --> 00:17:50.528 position:50% align:center
Draluc's album
with pics by Daddy!

00:17:50.612 --> 00:17:53.114 position:50% align:center
Take that thing home!
What's the point of it?!

00:17:53.198 --> 00:17:54.991 position:50% align:center
You guys don't even
show up in pictures!

00:17:55.075 --> 00:17:58.244 position:50% align:center
We do on a nice
camera if we try hard.

00:17:58.328 --> 00:18:01.039 position:50% align:center
My son was so adorable
when he was young.

00:18:01.122 --> 00:18:04.250 position:50% align:center
Because he was weak,
I worried a lot.

00:18:04.334 --> 00:18:07.253 position:50% align:center
But 200 years ago, we vampires
were much more at odds

00:18:07.337 --> 00:18:10.090 position:50% align:center
with humans than we are today.

00:18:10.173 --> 00:18:12.592 position:50% align:center
I swore that I would
protect that frail child

00:18:12.676 --> 00:18:14.094 position:50% align:center
until the very end.

00:18:14.177 --> 00:18:15.637 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Hm.

00:18:15.720 --> 00:18:18.306 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS] Well, cameras weren't
invented yet 200 years ago,

00:18:18.390 --> 00:18:20.475 position:50% align:center
so I don't haven't any pictures
of him from back then!

00:18:20.558 --> 00:18:22.018 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Then who cares?

00:18:22.102 --> 00:18:25.021 position:50% align:center
Here's my autobiography!
Just for your reference.

00:18:25.105 --> 00:18:27.565 position:50% align:center
And, if you insist,
I can also make an appear--

00:18:27.649 --> 00:18:30.193 position:50% align:center
Ow! [groans]

00:18:30.276 --> 00:18:32.112 position:50% align:center
You not dying
screws with my rhythm.

00:18:32.195 --> 00:18:33.363 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS] You didn't have
to say it like that,

00:18:33.446 --> 00:18:34.656 position:50% align:center
you little stripling!

00:18:34.739 --> 00:18:36.199 position:50% align:center
This is awful!

00:18:36.282 --> 00:18:38.952 position:50% align:center
Are you telling me that you
cause Draluc to die regularly?

00:18:39.035 --> 00:18:41.871 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] Shut up!
He dies on his own all the time!

00:18:41.955 --> 00:18:44.958 position:50% align:center
He's harder to keep alive
than a carnival goldfish!

00:18:45.041 --> 00:18:46.835 position:50% align:center
John, are you all
right in this place?

00:18:46.918 --> 00:18:49.045 position:50% align:center
Is this bastard doing
mean things to you?

00:18:49.129 --> 00:18:50.505 position:50% align:center
--[JOHN squeaking]
--[RONALDO] What the hell?

00:18:50.588 --> 00:18:52.132 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] I would never do
anything like that to John!

00:18:52.215 --> 00:18:53.633 position:50% align:center
[JOHN]
Mm...

00:18:53.717 --> 00:18:55.135 position:50% align:center
[JOHN grunts]

00:18:55.218 --> 00:18:57.095 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
John! No!

00:18:57.178 --> 00:19:00.348 position:50% align:center
John's eyes look so sad.
What did you do?!

00:19:00.432 --> 00:19:02.350 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
That was nothing! It was--

00:19:02.434 --> 00:19:03.685 position:50% align:center
I'm sorry, John!

00:19:03.768 --> 00:19:05.020 position:50% align:center
I won't allow this!

00:19:05.103 --> 00:19:07.272 position:50% align:center
I cannot let Draluc
stay with the likes of you!

00:19:07.355 --> 00:19:08.481 position:50% align:center
I'm taking him home!

00:19:08.565 --> 00:19:09.941 position:50% align:center
Fine, then take him home!

00:19:10.025 --> 00:19:12.819 position:50% align:center
It'll be a relief to get
rid of that pain in the ass.

00:19:12.902 --> 00:19:14.404 position:50% align:center
Ah...

00:19:14.487 --> 00:19:17.073 position:50% align:center
Your teamwork with that vampire
was surprisingly well-received.

00:19:17.157 --> 00:19:19.451 position:50% align:center
The editor-in-chief would
like to see more of that.

00:19:19.534 --> 00:19:21.619 position:50% align:center
I'm looking forward to it.

00:19:21.703 --> 00:19:23.121 position:50% align:center
Hold on, don't be rash;

00:19:23.204 --> 00:19:25.123 position:50% align:center
let's ask Draluc
what he wants to do.

00:19:25.206 --> 00:19:27.459 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS grunts]
Oh, right.

00:19:27.542 --> 00:19:28.793 position:50% align:center
But where is he?

00:19:28.877 --> 00:19:31.629 position:50% align:center
He hasn't been answering
any of my texts or calls.

00:19:31.713 --> 00:19:33.506 position:50% align:center
Could it be that
he's been kidnapped?

00:19:33.590 --> 00:19:35.091 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Let him leave the nest already!

00:19:35.175 --> 00:19:37.927 position:50% align:center
Be quiet! Anything could happen
to a child as cute as he is--

00:19:38.011 --> 00:19:39.054 position:50% align:center
[ODD CREATURE]
Excuse me.

00:19:39.137 --> 00:19:40.180 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO, DRAUS]
Hm?

00:19:40.263 --> 00:19:42.807 position:50% align:center
Oh, sorry, we're not open today.

00:19:42.891 --> 00:19:46.102 position:50% align:center
[ODD CREATURE] Hey there,
friend! Wanna trade adult DVDs?

00:19:50.065 --> 00:19:51.816 position:50% align:center
Check it out, Draluc's back.

00:19:51.900 --> 00:19:54.444 position:50% align:center
[ODD CREATURE] Father.
I love this town, let me stay.

00:19:54.527 --> 00:19:56.279 position:50% align:center
You think me stupid?

00:19:56.363 --> 00:19:58.865 position:50% align:center
Stop messing around!
I'm going to look for Draluc!

00:19:58.948 --> 00:20:01.743 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] Hey, wait up!
Fine, I'll go, too!

00:20:01.826 --> 00:20:03.536 position:50% align:center
Not here.

00:20:03.620 --> 00:20:05.080 position:50% align:center
Bummer.

00:20:05.163 --> 00:20:07.957 position:50% align:center
I guess we'll have to search
the places that dummy might go.

00:20:08.041 --> 00:20:10.877 position:50% align:center
Draluc? Oh, I haven't
seen him today.

00:20:10.960 --> 00:20:13.713 position:50% align:center
Tell him I want him to make me
pudding next time I do, though!

00:20:13.797 --> 00:20:16.091 position:50% align:center
Where's Draluc?
I haven't seen him.

00:20:16.174 --> 00:20:17.258 position:50% align:center
Maybe he's at the guild.

00:20:17.342 --> 00:20:18.551 position:50% align:center
[gasps] You're his dad?

00:20:18.635 --> 00:20:20.095 position:50% align:center
Oh, hello there.

00:20:20.178 --> 00:20:22.305 position:50% align:center
[MASTER] No, he hasn't
been here at all today.

00:20:22.389 --> 00:20:24.808 position:50% align:center
Oh, his hot milk tab
is growing, so send him by.

00:20:24.891 --> 00:20:26.059 position:50% align:center
And will you please tell him

00:20:26.142 --> 00:20:28.311 position:50% align:center
to stop calling me
"Mr. Bearded Lady Lover"?

00:20:28.395 --> 00:20:29.979 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Uh, yeah, sure.

00:20:30.063 --> 00:20:31.106 position:50% align:center
Draluc, huh?

00:20:31.189 --> 00:20:33.566 position:50% align:center
Sorry, I haven't
seen him this evening.

00:20:33.650 --> 00:20:36.361 position:50% align:center
Did you get into
a fight? [giggles]

00:20:36.444 --> 00:20:39.698 position:50% align:center
[HANDA] Hey, you idiot! I heard
you were looking for Draluc!

00:20:39.781 --> 00:20:41.074 position:50% align:center
Hey, come here!

00:20:41.157 --> 00:20:43.576 position:50% align:center
Don't ignore me! Hey!

00:20:43.660 --> 00:20:47.455 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] Damn it.
Where did that moron go?

00:20:47.539 --> 00:20:51.167 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS] Draluc, I came
to play with you! Draluc!

00:20:51.251 --> 00:20:54.004 position:50% align:center
Are you bored in this
castle all by yourself?

00:20:54.087 --> 00:20:55.255 position:50% align:center
I'm fine, Father.

00:20:55.338 --> 00:20:58.299 position:50% align:center
I have John and
my pile of games to play.

00:20:58.383 --> 00:20:59.968 position:50% align:center
You don't have
to worry about me.

00:21:00.051 --> 00:21:04.973 position:50% align:center
With just me and John here, it's
relaxing, and then I don't die.

00:21:05.974 --> 00:21:07.892 position:50% align:center
I've decided not to
bring him home.

00:21:07.976 --> 00:21:09.144 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO, JOHN grunt]

00:21:09.227 --> 00:21:10.353 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS]
I'm happy.

00:21:10.437 --> 00:21:14.024 position:50% align:center
My child is having
fun in this town.

00:21:14.107 --> 00:21:15.817 position:50% align:center
Ronaldo.

00:21:15.900 --> 00:21:18.778 position:50% align:center
It appears my son
has met a good human.

00:21:18.862 --> 00:21:20.321 position:50% align:center
--[RONALDO grunts]
--[SHINICHI] Oh, there he is!

00:21:20.405 --> 00:21:21.823 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:21:21.906 --> 00:21:23.199 position:50% align:center
[SHINICHI] We went to your
office, but you weren't there!

00:21:23.283 --> 00:21:24.909 position:50% align:center
We've been looking
for you, Ronaldo!

00:21:24.993 --> 00:21:26.411 position:50% align:center
Oh, sorry about that.

00:21:26.494 --> 00:21:27.871 position:50% align:center
Where is Dra--?

00:21:27.954 --> 00:21:29.122 position:50% align:center
Ah...

00:21:29.205 --> 00:21:31.708 position:50% align:center
He's transformed into
super shiny mud balls!

00:21:31.791 --> 00:21:36.004 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] What fun! I'm shining
like a string of pearls!

00:21:36.087 --> 00:21:38.590 position:50% align:center
[gasping]

00:21:38.673 --> 00:21:39.841 position:50% align:center
[DRAUS]
Dra--

00:21:39.924 --> 00:21:42.218 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Oh, shut up, damn it!

00:21:42.302 --> 00:21:45.722 position:50% align:center
[JOHN yelling]

00:21:45.805 --> 00:21:47.432 position:50% align:center
[JOHN grunting]

00:21:47.515 --> 00:21:48.516 position:50% align:center
That reminds me;

00:21:48.600 --> 00:21:50.352 position:50% align:center
how's the new manuscript
coming along?

00:21:50.435 --> 00:21:53.021 position:50% align:center
I lost my motivation
thanks to you guys.

00:21:53.104 --> 00:21:55.023 position:50% align:center
Hey, John, lemme
try the turntable.

00:21:55.106 --> 00:21:56.775 position:50% align:center
--[DRALUC gasps]
--[JOHN shrieks]

00:22:05.658 --> 00:22:07.952 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] We'll settle
this before dawn breaks!

00:22:08.036 --> 00:22:11.164 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] John! Do not worry!
We will save you!

00:22:13.041 --> 00:22:16.795 position:50% align:center line:10%
[DRALUC]
<i>The Vampire Dies In No Time</i> .